@Override public Story clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {     Story story = new Story().     story.fileName = this.fileName.     story.cases = new ArrayList<>().     for (Case caze : cases) {         story.cases.add(caze.clone()).     }     story.draft = draft.     story.description = description.     return story. }
